## Patient Portal Architecture (Tree Format)

Shareable architecture outline for the AI-assisted patient journey, including post-visit survey and long-range follow-up scheduling notifications.

## 1) System Landscape

Patient Portal Platform
├── Patient App (Web/Mobile)
│   ├── Symptom intake
│   ├── Appointment booking and rescheduling
│   ├── Check-in experience
│   ├── Reminder center
│   ├── Survey completion
│   └── Follow-up scheduling
├── API Gateway / Backend-for-Frontend (BFF)
│   ├── Auth and session handling
│   ├── Request orchestration
│   ├── Patient-facing APIs
│   └── Response shaping for mobile/web clients
├── AI Agent Layer
│   ├── Intake Assistant Agent
│   │   ├── Captures symptom/concern context
│   │   └── Structures data for scheduling and triage routing
│   ├── Scheduling Copilot
│   │   ├── Recommends provider options
│   │   └── Ranks appointment slots based on rules and patient preferences
│   ├── Waiting Room Assistant Agent
│   │   ├── Collects updates before provider arrives
│   │   └── Captures patient questions and concerns
│   ├── Provider Summary Generator
│   │   ├── Produces concise pre-visit summary
│   │   └── Highlights key context for focused appointments
│   └── Reminder Personalization Agent
│       ├── Adjusts reminder timing and tone
│       └── Honors consent and channel preferences
├── Scheduling System
│   ├── Provider availability calendar
│   ├── Appointment rules and constraints
│   ├── Booking / rescheduling engine
│   ├── Future schedule publication
│   └── Follow-up eligibility windows (6-12 months)
├── Notification and Engagement Service
│   ├── Push, SMS, email delivery
│   ├── Campaign and workflow templates
│   ├── Survey trigger workflows
│   └── Follow-up booking alerts
├── Event Bus + Workflow Orchestrator
│   ├── Lifecycle event publishing
│   ├── Async process coordination
│   ├── Retry and dead-letter handling
│   └── Idempotent workflow execution
├── External Integrations
│   ├── Maps / Traffic API
│   │   ├── Real-time travel estimates
│   │   └── Departure-time recommendations
│   └── Transportation Services
│       ├── Ride options/deep links
│       └── Late-arrival mitigation support
├── EHR / Provider Dashboard
│   ├── Encounter and status updates
│   ├── AI summary display
│   ├── Provider review workflow
│   └── Visit completion trigger source
└── Analytics and Reporting
    ├── Satisfaction trends
    ├── Follow-up conversion
    ├── No-show and lateness metrics
    └── Capacity and scheduling optimization insights

## 2) End-to-End Patient Journey

Patient Care Workflow
├── Step 1: Patient opens portal and enters symptom/concern
├── Step 2: AI suggests providers and appointment slots
├── Step 3: Patient schedules or reschedules appointment
├── Step 4: AI confirms booking and adds reminders/calendar hooks
├── Step 5: Day-of reminder checks traffic and suggests departure time
├── Step 6: Patient arrives and checks in
├── Step 7: AI waiting room assistant collects updates/questions
├── Step 8: AI creates summary for provider
├── Step 9: Provider reviews summary and conducts focused visit
└── Step 10: Post-visit engagement and continuity flow
├── 10.1 Visit completion event received.

## 3) Event-Driven Backbone

Appointment Lifecycle Events
├── AppointmentBooked
├── AppointmentRescheduled
├── ReminderScheduled
├── DayOfTrafficReminderSent
├── PatientCheckedIn
├── WaitingRoomDataCaptured
├── ProviderSummaryGenerated
├── VisitCompleted
├── PostVisitReminderSent
├── SurveyRequested
├── SurveyCompleted
├── FollowUpWindowStarted
├── ProviderScheduleOpened
├── FollowUpPromptSent
└── FollowUpBooked

Each Event Payload (Minimum)
├── event_id
├── event_type
├── aggregate_id (patient/appointment/encounter reference)
├── occurred_at
├── source_system
├── correlation_id
├── version
└── idempotency_key

## 4) AI Governance and Safety

AI Guardrails
├── Constrained recommendations (rule-first enforcement)
├── Structured output schemas
├── Clinical safety boundaries (advisory, not autonomous diagnosis)
├── Provider-in-the-loop review for visit summaries
├── Prompt/output auditability
└── Escalation paths for uncertain/high-risk cases

## 5) Security and Compliance

Healthcare Security Controls
├── Encryption in transit and at rest
├── Role-based and attribute-based access controls
├── Least-privilege data access for AI and services
├── Consent management (notifications, channels, survey)
├── Full audit logging
└── Data retention and deletion policies

## 6) Measurement Framework

Operational KPIs
├── Booking success rate
├── Notification delivery and engagement
├── Workflow failure and retry rates
└── AI fallback/error rates

Experience and Outcome KPIs
├── Survey completion rate
├── Patient satisfaction (CSAT/NPS)
├── No-show reduction
├── Follow-up prompt-to-book conversion
└── Continuity-of-care improvement over 6-12 months

## 7) Build Phases

Roadmap

├── Phase 1: Core scheduling + reminders
│   ├── Patient booking and rescheduling
│   ├── Scheduling integration
│   └── Notification baseline

├── Phase 2: AI-assisted visit prep
│   ├── Intake assistant
│   ├── Waiting room assistant
│   └── Provider summary generation

├── Phase 3: Post-visit engagement (new feature)
│   ├── Survey automation
│   ├── Follow-up window logic (6-12 months)
│   ├── Schedule-open monitoring
│   └── Direct follow-up self-scheduling

└── Phase 4: Optimization and scaling
    ├── Personalization tuning
    ├── Capacity-aware scheduling improvements
    └── Closed-loop quality and efficiency insights
